title: President Donald J. Trump Announces Great American Economic Revival Industry Groups – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Economy & Jobs	

Issued on:
April 14, 2020
Today, President Donald J. Trump announced many of the esteemed executives, economists, scholars, and industry leaders who together will form various Great American Economic Revival Industry Groups.  These bipartisan groups of American leaders will work together with the White House to chart the path forward toward a future of unparalleled American prosperity.  The health and wealth of America is the primary goal, and these groups will produce a more independent, self-sufficient, and resilient Nation.Agriculture
